Title: No Time To Rest
Description:
We have accomplished much since arriving here, but now is not the time to rest. Your efforts have helped us breach the upper level of the Thunder King's stronghold.

Now, I call on you to continue our campaign. Report to Scout Captain Daelin within Conqueror's Terrace. He will have further orders for you.
ObjectivesText: Locate Scout Captain Daelin within Conqueror's Terrace.
RewardText:
The Zandalari here are not to be under-estimated, $c. Powerful magic overwhelms this space.

We must be diligent in our efforts.
